seo_en: Landray OA, vulnerability detection, RCE, treexml
summary: 该插件用于检测蓝凌OA系统中的RCE（远程代码执行）漏洞，通过发送特定的HTTP请求并检查响应来确认是否存在漏洞。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect the RCE (Remote Code Execution) vulnerability in the Landray OA system by sending specific HTTP requests and checking the responses.
